title: HOUR 3- Frank Vogel Oct 14, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Frank Vogel Oct 14, 2020
description:
Frank Vogel tells Dan that the foods he missed most while in the NBA bubble was Pizza, Subs, and Ice cream. Frank admits to Dan that it really has not sunk in that he won a title in his first year as head coach of the Los Angeles Lakers. Frank says after he was fired; that he never would have thought that he would win a title with the Lakers in a million years.
